1
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:42,440
Scheme.

2
00:01:02,400 --> 00:01:03,520
Go to hell!

3
00:01:03,520 --> 00:01:04,160
Wait.

4
00:01:11,640 --> 00:01:13,320
Where did you come from?

5
00:01:13,760 --> 00:01:15,280
Thanks to

6
00:01:15,640 --> 00:01:17,080
the cats in your Tu Manor

7
00:01:17,080 --> 00:01:18,560
for digging the hole.

8
00:01:18,920 --> 00:01:20,400
Since you escaped,

9
00:01:20,640 --> 00:01:22,160
why did you come back?

10
00:01:22,760 --> 00:01:24,920
Do you want to die with them?

11
00:01:25,400 --> 00:01:26,520
As a constable,

12
00:01:26,520 --> 00:01:27,840
I must stick to my duty.

13
00:01:28,039 --> 00:01:29,320
I will never be afraid of death

14
00:01:29,320 --> 00:01:30,720
because of your Tu Manor.

15
00:01:32,120 --> 00:01:34,080
A mere Yingtian Prefecture Office

16
00:01:34,560 --> 00:01:36,840
dares to go against my Tu Manor?

17
00:01:37,320 --> 00:01:38,759
You overestimate yourselves.

18
00:01:38,759 --> 00:01:40,360
What if you add me?

19
00:01:48,920 --> 00:01:50,120
Nephew.

20
00:01:53,320 --> 00:01:55,200
I'm not too late, am I, Martial Uncle?

21
00:01:55,200 --> 00:01:56,160
If you were any later,

22
00:01:56,160 --> 00:01:57,890
I would have been killed by her.

23
00:01:58,960 --> 00:01:59,800
Old lady,

24
00:02:00,200 --> 00:02:01,080
did you think

25
00:02:01,240 --> 00:02:03,400
I only let Chief Qiu go back to the county office for reinforcements?

26
00:02:03,400 --> 00:02:04,330
To deal with you,

27
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:06,140
I have to use my ultimate move.

28
00:02:09,120 --> 00:02:11,240
Do you think bringing Gu Zhengyan here

29
00:02:11,240 --> 00:02:12,720
can intimidate me?

30
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:13,840
In your dreams!

31
00:02:14,920 --> 00:02:17,079
Ask my dragon-head cane

32
00:02:17,400 --> 00:02:18,720
if it agrees!

33
00:02:20,720 --> 00:02:21,720
Don't be a coward.

34
00:02:21,720 --> 00:02:22,720
Fight!

35
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:23,720
Martial Uncle.

36
00:02:23,720 --> 00:02:25,160
My son was murdered.

37
00:02:25,320 --> 00:02:27,040
I am avenging my son.

38
00:02:27,400 --> 00:02:28,530
Lord Vice Minister,

39
00:02:28,720 --> 00:02:30,850
you wouldn't try to stop me, would you?

40
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:32,860
Martial Uncle,

41
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:34,200
if the evidence is conclusive,

42
00:02:34,200 --> 00:02:36,400
she indeed has the right to deal with it.

43
00:02:37,960 --> 00:02:39,240
Revenge.

44
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:40,880
If I can prove that your son's death

45
00:02:40,880 --> 00:02:42,540
was caused by something else,

46
00:02:42,720 --> 00:02:44,980
then there's no need for revenge, right?

47
00:02:45,720 --> 00:02:47,640
Didn't you just clearly say

48
00:02:48,079 --> 00:02:50,320
my son was jointly murdered by them?

49
00:02:50,320 --> 00:02:51,960
They admitted it themselves.

50
00:02:51,960 --> 00:02:52,640
Could it be

51
00:02:52,920 --> 00:02:54,640
you want to go back on your word?

52
00:02:54,640 --> 00:02:56,760
What you see on the surface may not be the truth.

53
00:02:56,760 --> 00:02:58,360
The corpse has the final say.

54
00:02:58,360 --> 00:02:59,920
Smooth talker.

55
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:01,640
The truth is already out.

56
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:03,600
Saying anything is useless.

57
00:03:05,360 --> 00:03:06,160
Jianqin.

58
00:03:14,840 --> 00:03:15,720
In the cellar,

59
00:03:16,360 --> 00:03:18,360
besides Lai Lan and the murder weapon,

60
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:19,200
I also found a

61
00:03:19,200 --> 00:03:21,640
very important missing item from the scene.

62
00:03:21,640 --> 00:03:23,040
It is because of this item

63
00:03:23,120 --> 00:03:23,920
that I am sure

64
00:03:24,040 --> 00:03:25,240
there is no murderer.

65
00:03:25,640 --> 00:03:26,360
Could it be

66
00:03:26,640 --> 00:03:27,440
Father?

67
00:03:29,920 --> 00:03:31,079
Give me back my son.

68
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:33,480
This...

69
00:03:33,720 --> 00:03:34,880
This is not my son.

70
00:03:35,440 --> 00:03:36,120
Liu Chuan!

71
00:03:36,720 --> 00:03:38,440
Where is my son's head?

72
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:40,360
It just so happens that Jianqin

73
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:42,090
prepared pork head meat for me.

74
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:43,600
Because the scene is bloody,

75
00:03:43,600 --> 00:03:45,079
I will use this to explain.

76
00:03:46,120 --> 00:03:47,000
Ladies and gentlemen,

77
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:47,640
next,

78
00:03:47,640 --> 00:03:49,320
I will reveal the truth.

79
00:03:49,920 --> 00:03:51,480
According to the First Madam's confession,

80
00:03:51,480 --> 00:03:54,280
she hit the back of the deceased's head with a vase.

81
00:03:54,320 --> 00:03:55,440
But on the back of the deceased's head,

82
00:03:55,440 --> 00:03:57,000
no injuries were found,

83
00:03:57,200 --> 00:03:59,130
not even a subcutaneous hematoma.

84
00:03:59,920 --> 00:04:01,680
The eyeballs protruded from the sockets.

85
00:04:01,680 --> 00:04:03,540
But not caused by external force.

86
00:04:03,720 --> 00:04:06,320
Generally, if the back of the head suffers a strong impact,

87
00:04:06,320 --> 00:04:08,480
the shockwave would cause the intracranial brain tissue

88
00:04:08,480 --> 00:04:10,920
to force the eyeball out of the socket,

89
00:04:11,360 --> 00:04:14,160
resulting in the eyeball protruding from the socket.

90
00:04:14,160 --> 00:04:15,420
However, in this case,

91
00:04:15,520 --> 00:04:17,200
both eyeballs should protrude,

92
00:04:17,200 --> 00:04:18,360
instead of one protruding

93
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:20,360
and the other remaining unchanged.

94
00:04:20,720 --> 00:04:21,450
In addition,

95
00:04:21,760 --> 00:04:24,120
the human eye socket consists of seven bones.

96
00:04:24,120 --> 00:04:26,800
Due to the strong impact on the head,

97
00:04:27,160 --> 00:04:29,520
the bones at the bottom of the eye socket would be shattered,

98
00:04:29,520 --> 00:04:32,360
thus causing the eyeball to burst out of the socket.

99
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:33,200
So,

100
00:04:33,840 --> 00:04:34,720
it's highly likely the deceased had

101
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:37,120
a space-occupying lesion in the brain.

102
00:04:39,159 --> 00:04:39,880
Cerebral edema,

103
00:04:39,880 --> 00:04:40,760
brain abscess,

104
00:04:40,760 --> 00:04:41,960
brain mass, and so on.

105
00:04:42,320 --> 00:04:44,560
These would create a mass in the brain,

106
00:04:44,560 --> 00:04:46,320
causing increased intracranial pressure.

107
00:04:46,320 --> 00:04:47,960
The brain tissue under pressure

108
00:04:47,960 --> 00:04:49,520
would transmit this pressure out

109
00:04:49,520 --> 00:04:50,800
through the orbital fissures,

110
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:52,159
compressing the eyeballs

111
00:04:52,159 --> 00:04:54,159
and forcing them out of the sockets.

112
00:04:55,159 --> 00:04:56,420
Before Master Tu died,

113
00:04:56,680 --> 00:04:58,360
did he have headaches, fevers,

114
00:04:58,360 --> 00:05:00,120
or symptoms like vomiting?

115
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:05,680
He did.

116
00:05:07,560 --> 00:05:09,040
Then we can now be certain

117
00:05:09,320 --> 00:05:10,320
that Master Tu highly likely

118
00:05:10,320 --> 00:05:11,760
died from his own illness.

119
00:05:11,760 --> 00:05:12,960
The brain abscess

120
00:05:12,960 --> 00:05:14,820
means there is no murderer at all.

121
00:05:18,280 --> 00:05:19,080
Keep the pork away.

122
00:05:19,080 --> 00:05:20,200
I'm waiting to eat it with my wine.

123
00:05:20,200 --> 00:05:21,320
Yes, young master.

124
00:05:24,080 --> 00:05:25,480
Nonsense!

125
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:28,380
How can my son be compared to a pig's head?

126
00:05:28,520 --> 00:05:30,450
You are clearly talking nonsense!

127
00:05:30,520 --> 00:05:31,580
Then do an autopsy.

128
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:33,120
Only by doing an autopsy

129
00:05:33,120 --> 00:05:35,120
will the truth be revealed.

130
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:37,000
My son was murdered,

131
00:05:37,680 --> 00:05:39,400
and you want to ruin his body?

132
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:40,760
Wishful thinking!

133
00:05:40,760 --> 00:05:42,520
I have made it very clear to you.

134
00:05:42,520 --> 00:05:43,159
Only through an autopsy

135
00:05:43,159 --> 00:05:44,760
can we know the cause of your son's death.

136
00:05:44,760 --> 00:05:46,480
Without an autopsy, there is no truth.

137
00:05:46,480 --> 00:05:47,720
There is no murderer, yet you insist on catching one.

138
00:05:47,720 --> 00:05:49,000
Is this what you want?

139
00:05:49,280 --> 00:05:50,120
I don't care.

140
00:05:50,720 --> 00:05:52,180
My son died so tragically.

141
00:05:52,360 --> 00:05:54,159
Someone must pay with their life.

142
00:05:54,159 --> 00:05:55,820
If you don't get out of the way,

143
00:05:56,120 --> 00:05:57,159
I'll kill you first.

144
00:05:57,159 --> 00:05:57,800
Old Madam,

145
00:05:57,880 --> 00:05:58,560
Uncle,

146
00:05:58,800 --> 00:06:00,920
Young Master Liu speaks with good reason and evidence.

147
00:06:00,920 --> 00:06:02,800
Even if you have the power to establish a court and punish crimes,

148
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:04,660
you can't create a wrongful case.

149
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:07,480
The dragon head bestowed by the Emperor is here.

150
00:06:07,480 --> 00:06:09,140
Whoever dares to touch my son,

151
00:06:09,200 --> 00:06:10,480
I will take their life.

152
00:06:12,160 --> 00:06:12,760
Nephew.

153
00:06:12,760 --> 00:06:13,920
Do you have any Imperial Sword

154
00:06:13,920 --> 00:06:15,120
to confront her with?

155
00:06:15,520 --> 00:06:16,520
I certainly

156
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:17,320
have a way.

157
00:06:17,600 --> 00:06:19,130
I won't let you down, Uncle.

158
00:06:20,520 --> 00:06:22,250
Liu Chuan, receive the decree.

159
00:06:22,320 --> 00:06:23,450
By Imperial Decree,

160
00:06:23,520 --> 00:06:25,200
Liu Chuan, the coroner of Yingtian Prefecture,

161
00:06:25,200 --> 00:06:26,520
is extraordinarily wise and brave.

162
00:06:26,520 --> 00:06:26,960
I

163
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:30,080
appreciate your merit in purging Eunuch Qin's faction,

164
00:06:30,080 --> 00:06:30,680
and specially bestow upon you

165
00:06:30,680 --> 00:06:32,520
the items left by Lord Zhuoran.

166
00:06:37,400 --> 00:06:38,000
Uncle,

167
00:06:38,400 --> 00:06:41,659
these are all the dissecting instruments of Lord Zhuoran.

168
00:06:41,880 --> 00:06:44,320
These are things that only exist in modern times.

169
00:06:44,320 --> 00:06:45,800
Lord Zhuoran is indeed...

170
00:06:46,440 --> 00:06:48,360
Specially granting Liu Chuan the Willow Blade.

171
00:06:48,360 --> 00:06:49,290
With this blade,

172
00:06:49,480 --> 00:06:51,520
he may dissect any corpse in the realm

173
00:06:51,520 --> 00:06:53,200
and solve unsolved cases.

174
00:06:53,280 --> 00:06:54,520
No taboos shall apply.

175
00:06:54,520 --> 00:06:55,480
Respect this.

176
00:06:55,960 --> 00:06:57,000
Got it.

177
00:06:57,720 --> 00:06:59,650
It seems the Emperor has a good eye.

178
00:07:05,280 --> 00:07:06,080
Old lady,

179
00:07:06,640 --> 00:07:08,770
your cane is meant to scare the living.

180
00:07:08,920 --> 00:07:09,920
This blade of mine

181
00:07:09,960 --> 00:07:11,280
is meant to greet the dead.

182
00:07:11,280 --> 00:07:12,280
So by the looks of it,

183
00:07:12,280 --> 00:07:14,440
your son should be under my jurisdiction.

184
00:07:14,440 --> 00:07:15,170
Gu Zhengyan,

185
00:07:15,680 --> 00:07:17,810
how dare you forge an imperial decree?

186
00:07:17,880 --> 00:07:20,000
How would I dare to forge an imperial decree?

187
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:21,600
If Madam doesn't believe it,

188
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:22,660
you can inspect it.

189
00:07:29,200 --> 00:07:30,400
It is real.

190
00:07:32,480 --> 00:07:33,720
Even so,

191
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:35,520
as his mother,

192
00:07:35,960 --> 00:07:38,760
I will not allow anyone to desecrate my son's body.

193
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:41,120
As my father's only son,

194
00:07:41,240 --> 00:07:42,920
I agree to let Master Liu perform the autopsy

195
00:07:42,920 --> 00:07:44,050
to reveal the truth.

196
00:07:44,159 --> 00:07:45,159
How dare you!

197
00:07:45,360 --> 00:07:46,159
Grandmother,

198
00:07:46,400 --> 00:07:48,400
do not forget the Tu family's rules.

199
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:50,520
I am the only male in the Tu family.

200
00:07:50,520 --> 00:07:52,450
I am the true head of the household.

201
00:07:52,520 --> 00:07:53,600
You are a woman.

202
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:56,260
Naturally, it is not your place to speak.

203
00:07:58,520 --> 00:07:59,720
This is what they call

204
00:07:59,840 --> 00:08:02,000
getting hit by a bullet you fired years ago.

205
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:03,600
Right between the eyebrows.

206
00:08:04,080 --> 00:08:05,080
Old Madam,

207
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:07,120
you certainly wouldn't have thought

208
00:08:07,120 --> 00:08:08,520
that one day

209
00:08:08,520 --> 00:08:12,450
you would suffer the backlash of this rule of favoring boys over girls.

210
00:08:21,320 --> 00:08:23,120
Losing a son in your later years,

211
00:08:23,120 --> 00:08:25,450
I express my deepest sympathy and regret.

212
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:28,160
But my insistence on an autopsy to find out the truth

213
00:08:28,160 --> 00:08:30,960
is truly the greatest closure and respect for you.

214
00:08:31,120 --> 00:08:32,250
But the one I respect

215
00:08:32,559 --> 00:08:33,440
is not this

216
00:08:33,520 --> 00:08:35,039
firmly bound by worldly rules

217
00:08:35,039 --> 00:08:37,039
and indiscriminating Old Madam Tu,

218
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:39,280
but that

219
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:42,120
female general who was not inferior to men.

220
00:08:42,880 --> 00:08:44,480
The me from back then.

221
00:09:19,880 --> 00:09:20,920
Whoever you are,

222
00:09:21,280 --> 00:09:22,880
you will get the truth today.

223
00:10:46,040 --> 00:10:47,640
There is indeed no murderer.

224
00:10:47,720 --> 00:10:48,360
Master Tu

225
00:10:48,640 --> 00:10:50,440
simply died of a sudden illness.

226
00:10:50,680 --> 00:10:51,940
This can be considered

227
00:10:51,960 --> 00:10:54,020
retribution for his many evil deeds.

228
00:10:56,920 --> 00:10:58,720
Now that the truth has been revealed,

229
00:10:58,720 --> 00:10:59,980
the case can be closed.

230
00:11:00,240 --> 00:11:00,840
Guards!

231
00:11:09,400 --> 00:11:10,080
Auntie.

232
00:11:10,440 --> 00:11:11,300
Second Mother.

233
00:11:12,920 --> 00:11:13,800
Brother,

234
00:11:13,800 --> 00:11:14,880
let's go out first

235
00:11:15,760 --> 00:11:17,490
and give the old lady some time.

236
00:11:21,520 --> 00:11:22,320
Wait.

237
00:11:22,880 --> 00:11:23,740
Second Mother.

238
00:11:32,520 --> 00:11:34,440
Although you are not the murderers,

239
00:11:34,440 --> 00:11:35,440
forging the scene

240
00:11:35,440 --> 00:11:36,640
and destroying the corpse

241
00:11:36,640 --> 00:11:37,970
still makes you guilty.

242
00:11:38,200 --> 00:11:38,960
Don't worry.

243
00:11:39,520 --> 00:11:41,520
My nephew will treat you leniently.

244
00:11:46,440 --> 00:11:47,080
Yunmeng.

245
00:11:47,880 --> 00:11:49,080
Mr. Liu is right.

246
00:11:49,840 --> 00:11:52,000
After all, because of our moment of weakness,

247
00:11:52,000 --> 00:11:53,200
we almost killed you,

248
00:11:54,000 --> 00:11:56,330
and we should receive our due punishment.

249
00:11:58,040 --> 00:11:59,500
It's justice from heaven.

250
00:12:00,160 --> 00:12:00,720
Yunmeng.

251
00:12:00,920 --> 00:12:01,520
Second Mother,

252
00:12:01,520 --> 00:12:03,000
I am sorry.

253
00:12:03,200 --> 00:12:04,060
Second Mother.

254
00:12:05,280 --> 00:12:06,080
Child,

255
00:12:06,640 --> 00:12:07,900
take care of yourself.

256
00:12:11,400 --> 00:12:12,400
Mr. Liu,

257
00:12:12,840 --> 00:12:14,440
thank you for saving my life.

258
00:12:14,880 --> 00:12:15,680
In addition,

259
00:12:16,080 --> 00:12:17,280
on behalf of the pawned wives

260
00:12:17,280 --> 00:12:19,680
cruelly treated by the Tu family for generations,

261
00:12:19,680 --> 00:12:20,540
I also thank you

262
00:12:20,600 --> 00:12:22,440
for clearing their names.

263
00:12:26,120 --> 00:12:27,320
Take them away first.

264
00:12:28,440 --> 00:12:28,960
Yunmeng.

265
00:12:28,960 --> 00:12:29,820
Second Mother.

266
00:12:31,920 --> 00:12:33,200
It was you

267
00:12:34,960 --> 00:12:36,400
who trapped me here

268
00:12:36,560 --> 00:12:37,760
for decades.

269
00:12:38,840 --> 00:12:41,040
You stripped me of my name,

270
00:12:41,840 --> 00:12:43,840
my passion,

271
00:12:44,480 --> 00:12:46,400
my past,

272
00:12:47,000 --> 00:12:49,480
my hope,

273
00:12:55,320 --> 00:12:57,720
and even myself.

274
00:13:01,120 --> 00:13:02,320
Even I,

275
00:13:03,120 --> 00:13:05,680
like the rest of the world,

276
00:13:06,480 --> 00:13:08,160
have forgotten

277
00:13:09,320 --> 00:13:10,240
myself.

278
00:13:13,520 --> 00:13:14,120
Grandma.

279
00:13:16,760 --> 00:13:17,320
Grandma.

280
00:13:18,640 --> 00:13:21,720
I'm not just the Tu family's daughter-in-law,

281
00:13:21,880 --> 00:13:23,440
my husband's wife,

282
00:13:23,440 --> 00:13:25,240
my children's mother,

283
00:13:25,240 --> 00:13:27,640
or my daughter-in-law's mother-in-law.

284
00:13:28,440 --> 00:13:30,120
I was once

285
00:13:30,760 --> 00:13:31,960
charging into enemy lines,

286
00:13:31,960 --> 00:13:35,320
a general fighting bloody battles.

287
00:13:39,720 --> 00:13:43,440
They also made me just like them,

288
00:13:44,480 --> 00:13:46,080
feared

289
00:13:46,480 --> 00:13:48,080
and hated.

290
00:13:50,320 --> 00:13:51,480
Why?

291
00:13:51,800 --> 00:13:53,360
Why?

292
00:13:56,480 --> 00:13:59,880
Why?

293
00:14:08,360 --> 00:14:09,200
Take him away.

294
00:14:25,000 --> 00:14:27,200
For the so-called continuation of the family line.

295
00:14:27,200 --> 00:14:28,800
They don't hesitate to treat women

296
00:14:28,800 --> 00:14:29,920
as breeding tools,

297
00:14:30,840 --> 00:14:32,120
dominating them at will,

298
00:14:32,120 --> 00:14:34,050
and even trampling on their lives.

299
00:14:34,120 --> 00:14:35,240
But regardless of gender

300
00:14:35,240 --> 00:14:36,520
or social status,

301
00:14:36,840 --> 00:14:38,320
everyone should be equal.

302
00:14:40,000 --> 00:14:42,240
Can gender equality really be achieved?

303
00:14:42,240 --> 00:14:42,920
Of course.

304
00:14:43,560 --> 00:14:45,640
That's how it is in my era.

305
00:14:46,400 --> 00:14:48,040
Then I will change this era.

306
00:14:53,000 --> 00:14:54,320
You must live well.

307
00:14:54,600 --> 00:14:56,040
Be a free, happy,

308
00:14:56,320 --> 00:14:57,450
and carefree woman.

309
00:14:58,000 --> 00:14:59,280
Please thank Mr. Liu

310
00:14:59,520 --> 00:15:00,920
and everyone else for me.

311
00:15:13,520 --> 00:15:15,280
I hope she can live a good life.

312
00:15:21,600 --> 00:15:23,000
I sold my family property

313
00:15:23,080 --> 00:15:25,040
just to help poor women in the world

314
00:15:25,120 --> 00:15:26,720
by building charity houses.

315
00:15:26,840 --> 00:15:27,920
I hope such things

316
00:15:27,920 --> 00:15:29,320
will never happen again.

317
00:15:30,640 --> 00:15:31,440
Also,

318
00:15:32,840 --> 00:15:33,840
Mr. Liu,

319
00:15:33,960 --> 00:15:35,290
I also want to thank you.

320
00:15:35,880 --> 00:15:36,960
You must accept

321
00:15:37,120 --> 00:15:38,200
this small gift.

322
00:15:41,520 --> 00:15:43,080
But I still believe

323
00:15:43,320 --> 00:15:45,450
that everything happens for a reason.

324
00:15:47,040 --> 00:15:48,320
Breaking feudal superstitions

325
00:15:48,320 --> 00:15:49,600
is a long and arduous task.

326
00:15:49,600 --> 00:15:51,040
I was just doing my duty.

327
00:15:51,400 --> 00:15:52,000
Besides,

328
00:15:52,440 --> 00:15:54,240
this is all to the credit of my leader.

329
00:15:54,240 --> 00:15:55,440
You should thank her.

330
00:15:55,720 --> 00:15:56,360
Qiuyue,

331
00:15:56,600 --> 00:15:58,130
I will naturally thank her.

332
00:15:58,680 --> 00:15:59,840
But this item

333
00:16:00,080 --> 00:16:01,410
can only be given to you.

334
00:16:06,920 --> 00:16:07,520
Yunmeng.

335
00:16:10,000 --> 00:16:11,480
Last time you told me,

336
00:16:11,640 --> 00:16:13,700
what did you mean by I'm not Liu Chuan?

337
00:16:14,920 --> 00:16:16,480
Maybe I was wrong.

338
00:16:16,920 --> 00:16:17,600
Perhaps

339
00:16:17,720 --> 00:16:18,960
it's my intuition.

340
00:16:32,880 --> 00:16:34,520
Isn't this the relic

341
00:16:34,760 --> 00:16:36,520
from Yunmeng's mother?

342
00:16:37,440 --> 00:16:38,520
She said

343
00:16:39,080 --> 00:16:41,440
she would only give it to the one she loves.

344
00:16:42,240 --> 00:16:42,800
I... I...

345
00:16:42,800 --> 00:16:44,480
I don't know why she gave me this.

346
00:16:44,480 --> 00:16:45,120
You...

347
00:16:45,200 --> 00:16:46,460
What's wrong with you?

348
00:16:46,520 --> 00:16:47,200
I'm fine.

349
00:16:47,920 --> 00:16:48,920
It must be very precious.

350
00:16:48,920 --> 00:16:50,120
Just keep it safe.

351
00:16:50,640 --> 00:16:52,170
Make sure you don't lose it.

352
00:16:52,520 --> 00:16:53,440
Let go of the young master.

353
00:16:53,440 --> 00:16:54,120
Mr. Liu.

354
00:16:58,280 --> 00:16:59,800
Congratulations on solving another major case.

355
00:16:59,800 --> 00:17:01,600
I came specifically to reward you,

356
00:17:01,600 --> 00:17:04,119
and I want to bring your French fries

357
00:17:04,119 --> 00:17:05,720
into Baoyue Restaurant

358
00:17:06,119 --> 00:17:07,319
to sell together.

359
00:17:10,480 --> 00:17:11,010
Let's go.

360
00:17:11,200 --> 00:17:12,280
We can talk while we drink.

361
00:17:12,280 --> 00:17:12,880
Boss,

362
00:17:12,880 --> 00:17:13,839
I need to take tomorrow off.

363
00:17:13,839 --> 00:17:14,720
How dare you.

364
00:18:00,080 --> 00:18:02,360
The master started to have headaches

365
00:18:02,480 --> 00:18:04,480
after he got the secret recipe for a son.

366
00:18:04,480 --> 00:18:06,520
But the person who gave him the recipe

367
00:18:06,520 --> 00:18:08,120
had a very mysterious look.

368
00:18:08,320 --> 00:18:10,180
I can't remember clearly either.

369
00:18:11,880 --> 00:18:13,120
Your deaths

370
00:18:13,520 --> 00:18:14,520
must be related.

371
00:18:19,680 --> 00:18:21,440
Liu Chuan from Yingtian Prefecture

372
00:18:21,440 --> 00:18:23,040
is confirmed dead.

373
00:18:23,280 --> 00:18:25,120
This identical one now

374
00:18:25,440 --> 00:18:27,280
is definitely an imposter.

375
00:18:28,040 --> 00:18:29,520
Interesting.

376
00:18:30,200 --> 00:18:31,930
Let's see what he's capable of,

377
00:18:32,320 --> 00:18:34,800
and if he's the one I've been looking for.
